channel.title: Versions...?
channel.description:
Sorry if there's a thread on this, I looked around and looked at all the stickies. I haven't touched RuneScape in...three years? All my posts that were on here have long since been deleted, and I haven't even played with Java since then.
Basically, last time I was here, CheezScape was one of the most common servers. I'm looking to set up a new one (not a base, something already mostly done.)
What's with all the 500+ versions? What are the differences? And which ones are most completed? I don't really need pvp/clan wars/etc. I just want something for just me to play alone.
Thanks for not flaming.
